{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.200", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.920", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.400", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich schlie\u00dfe mich dem Dank an die Behindertenbeauftragte uneingeschr\u00e4nkt an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.000", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.480", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau \u00adBentele, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.840", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.640", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie in den letzten Jahren f\u00fcr Menschen mit Behinderungen und f\u00fcr unser Land geleistet haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.040", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leider ist es einigen Menschen drau\u00dfen heute nicht m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.520", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genau diese Debatte zu verfolgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.440", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil der Geb\u00e4rdensprachdolmetscher auf dem Livestream des Deutschen Bundestages nur bis 12\u00a0Uhr \u00fcbertragen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.760", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch so viel geh\u00f6rt zur Wahrheit dazu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.640", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von daher: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Guten Tag."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.080", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist zun\u00e4chst erfreulich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.800", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir heute hier im Parlament \u00fcber den Ausweis f\u00fcr Menschen mit Behinderungen sprechen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.840", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dadurch r\u00fccken endlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.520", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn auch nur kurzfristig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.560", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diejenigen in den Mittelpunkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in ihrer gesellschaftlichen Teilhabe noch immer sehr eingeschr\u00e4nkt sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.840", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leider muss ich zugleich aber konstatieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.560", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Debatte die tiefer gehenden Probleme von Menschen mit Behinderungen \u00fcberdeckt und sogar von ihnen ablenkt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Initiative der FDP-Fraktion ist faktisch ein Etikettenschwindel; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.680", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.480", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen der FDP, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.040", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schauen wir doch mal in Ihr Wahlprogramm. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie fordern \u201eein Wunsch- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.440", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Wahlrecht auf Leistungen zur Teilhabe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.280", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel freie Wahl von Wohnort und Wohnform kostenneutral innerhalb eines vorgegebenen Budgets\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.960", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage Ihnen sehr deutlich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.400", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die volle und wirksame Teilhabe von Menschen mit Behinderungen ist nicht kostenneutral und schon gar nicht umsonst zu haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.600", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die UN-Behindertenrechtskonvention stellt Forderungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.040", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir m\u00fcssen sie nur noch umsetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.440", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir reden hier von Menschenrechten und nicht von Kosten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.760", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eingespart werden k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bundestag sollte sich mit der tats\u00e4chlichen Lebenssituation der Betroffenen auseinandersetzen und wirkliche Verbesserungen schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.480", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei sollte sich die Bundesregierung an ihrer eigenen Definition von Teilhabe orientieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.400", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Bundesministerium f\u00fcr Arbeit und Soziales schreibt wie folgt:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.440", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen mit Behinderungen wollen genauso leben wie nichtbehinderte Menschen auch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.080", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber bewegen wir uns nur ein paar Schritte von hier entfernt im Bundestag\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen nicht einmal den Komplex verlassen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.120", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist egal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es nun das Paul-L\u00f6be-Haus oder das Jakob-Kaiser-Haus ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das reicht schon aus\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.200", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sollte sehr schnell klar werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.320", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Bar\u00adrierefreiheit auch dort nur ein frommer Wunsch ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das alleinige Einsetzen von Rampen und der Einbau von Fahrst\u00fchlen bedeuten noch lange nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.080", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die R\u00e4umlichkeiten f\u00fcr alle Menschen erreichbar und nutzbar sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.000", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Bentele sprach die Gruppe an: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.120", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen mit Sehbeeintr\u00e4chtigungen haben kaum eine Chance, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.680", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich hier selbst zurechtzufinden und zu orientieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.040", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es geht nicht nur um die Gestaltung von Geb\u00e4uden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch um die von Bahnh\u00f6fen und um die des Bahnverkehrs. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.360", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will heute an dieser Stelle gar nicht auf die uns\u00e4gliche Diskussion des Bundesverkehrsministeriums eingehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welches fordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.200", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die unterschiedliche H\u00f6he von Bahnsteigen zu vereinheitlichen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.080", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir ist es relativ egal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.720", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob Bahnsteige in Deutschland \u00fcberall die gleiche H\u00f6he haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.480", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir ist wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.520", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass alle barrierefrei und damit nutzbar f\u00fcr alle sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch bei der Umsetzung des Bundesteilhabegesetzes\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.480", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darauf sind die Vorredner schon eingegangen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.560", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist noch Luft nach oben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.600", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier liegt noch einige Arbeit vor uns. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.640", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ich an meinen Alltag als Lehrer zur\u00fcckblicke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.880", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann kann ich nur feststellen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.360", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In vielen K\u00f6pfen sind die Worte \u201eIntegration\u201c und \u201eInklusion\u201c noch gar nicht angekommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.920", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leider riecht selbst das h\u00f6chste parlamentarische Gremium in Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Bundestag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.760", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.200", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diesbez\u00fcglich in Teilen widerlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.880", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier im Hause sitzt nach eigenen Aussagen ein \u201eg\u00e4riger Haufen\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.240", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser bringt in schlechter Regelm\u00e4\u00dfigkeit braun-blaue Sumpfblasen hervor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.480", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die bisher nach unserer Auffassung stinkendste Blase stieg vor etwa einem Monat empor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.080", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Rahmen einer Kleinen Anfrage der AfD zeigt sich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.400", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was diese vermeintlichen Demokraten von Menschen mit Behinderungen halten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.520", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eUnertr\u00e4gliche Menschen- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.720", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Lebensfeindlichkeit\u201c war in einer Zeitungsannonce der Sozialverb\u00e4nde in der \u201eFrankfurter Allgemeinen Sonntagszeitung\u201c zu lesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.920", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn in der Anfrage wurden vermeintliche Zusammenh\u00e4nge zwischen Inzucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.040", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Behinderung und Migration intendiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.320", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist widerlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.720", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch wenn es der Bundesregierung in diesem Sumpf augenscheinlich recht unbehaglich wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.960", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00f6chte ich die geistigen Wurzeln dieser perfiden Anfrage klar benennen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.160", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Behinderungen als vermeidbares \u00dcbel darzustellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.200", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist v\u00f6llig inakzeptabel."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.000", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pellmann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.960", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erlauben Sie eine Zwischenfrage oder -bemerkung?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.520", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.520", 
   "children": [], 
